      • callFunctionInBackground

        public static <T> void callFunctionInBackground(String functionName,
                                Map<String,?> params,
                                FunctionCallback<T> callback)
        Calls a cloud function in the background.
        参数:
        functionName - The cloud function to call.
        params - The parameters to send to the cloud function. This map can contain anything that could be placed in a MLObject except for MLObjects themselves.
        callback - The callback that will be called when the cloud function has returned.
